d you get through those horrible traps to arrive here?'),(332,'Please don\'t be mistaken. Although I have settled here, I\'m not clear the origin of those traps.'),(333,'I\'m also obssessed by the traps?? it\'s a mystery who created them.'),(334,'Wait, there must be something to appear. Is it you guys who do this? Do you guys want to hurt me?'),(335,'Don\'t you do that? Anyway, you are all strong warriors.'),(336,'You guys make me think about a girl named Jendaluke'),(337,'Her power is the greatest. I was getting to respect her when she visited me for saving her nation.'),(338,'She is so young to be here for saving the nation.'),(339,'Why are you guys visiting me? You should know that it\'s very dangerous here.'),(340,'Now I\'m so headache that I cannot help you for the moment.'),(341,'Well, you should not have ejected these guests who were asking for help. It\'s so rude.'),(342,'Please don\'t blame me. The old make such mistakes sometimes. After a while, watch the ballon go up,hahaha!'),(343,'Great, wonderful! Let me see.'),(344,'I really cannot stand the fragrance from your guys.'),(345,'It\'s a humiliation that I\'m defeated by you guys.'),(346,'It\'s dangerous here. Get out of here?? Oh, I can\'t hold on.'),(347,'Well! I felt so bad?? You guys\' expressions are so ridiculous. I\'d like to play more tricks on you more.'),(348,'Stop! Stop attack! I didn\'t mean to. Well?? I thought everything was well, but evilness still exists, cannot get rid of.'),(349,'Things which have happened cannot be redeemed. Do you want to make a compromise with me now ?'),(350,'The power which Jendaluke wanted to have?? Don\'t you want to know? '),(351,'Then, Jendaluke refused my request. However, I believe you will not absolutely.'),(352,'Then, I gave her the power she wanted at the expense of her flesh and blood. I don\'t think the requirement is high.'),(353,'I was hurt badly so I decided to cut off all connections with outside. That\'s why I designed all of these traps.'),(354,'I abandoned all my own glories!'),(355,'Look! I created lives with my power. You all can get renascence.'),(356,'Ah? What\'s wrong? Is it not enough? If no human child\'s blood, perfect life cannot be created!'),(357,'Once we had Jendaluke\'s blood?? By the way, try some of your blood, although it\'s not that pure.'),(358,'I will creat perfect life. Your blood is flowing in my body, you guys should be feel proud.'),(359,'The blood of like you guys??. You don\'t need to feel sorry. I\'ll take care of everything. '),(360,'I really don\'t understand, why are you feeling so hopeful for life? Anyway, everybody will die, turning to dust'),(361,'Ask her who she is.'),(362,'You\'d better go back. It\'s good for you.'),(363,'I warned you, it\'s a dangerous place. Now, I\'m?? Ah??'),(364,'Ahaha, the shell is finally removed.'),(365,'Magic was used for bringing you memorable things. But now, it seems no useful.'),(366,'Have you guys ever seen that? This is a real masterwork. Look at yourselves who are fighting with illusions, so poor.'),(367,'How\'s your feeling? Is it great to be tricked?'),(368,'No, please, please let me go!'),(369,'From now on, nothing is illusion.'),(370,'OK, follow me!'),(371,'I\'m tired of people who play double characters or things like just waiting for food.'),(372,'脰禄脫脨路脌脢脴路陆碌脛脕陋脙脣虏脜驴脡脪脭脢鹿脫脙隆拢'),(373,'脥卢脪芒脥脣鲁枚脕陋脙脣'),(374,'戮脺戮酶脥脣鲁枚脕陋脙脣'),(375,'脥卢脪芒脥脣鲁枚脕陋脙脣'),(376,'戮脺戮酶脥脣鲁枚脕陋脙脣'),(377,'卤禄脕陋脙脣脕梅路脜隆拢'),(378,'脨脨禄谩卤禄脕陋脙脣隆拢'),(379,'脕陋脙脣脪脩陆芒脡垄隆拢');
